FBIS4-39958 "drsov113_b_94005" FBIS-SOV-94-113 Daily Report 13 Jun 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues `Russia's Democratic Choice Party' Holds Founding Congress `Russia's Democratic Choice Party' Holds Founding Congress Gaydar Elected Chairman LD1306074594 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0719 GMT 13 Jun 94 LD1306074594 Moscow ITAR-TASS English BFN [By ITAR-TASS] [Text] Moscow June 13 TASS -- The Russia's Democratic Choice Party has voted in favour of economist Yegor Gaydar being party chairman and Oleg Boyko, head of the National Credit Bank and chief of the Olby concern, chairman of the party's executive committee. Boyko promised to contribute to creating an efficient organizational structure attracting more entrepreneurs to its ranks and boosting the party's publicity activity.
